metadata.description:
He looked down at a puddle that had formed at his feet, and in the ripples he could see his own face now.



The black and yellow half-and-half metal helmet is shaped like a hockey mask. Behind the head are two thin cloth straps flying in the wind and rain, like Rambo's headband. The left eye of the mask is a red diamond eyepiece, and the right half of the mask is completely black without a crack.
